00:06:30.940 --> 00:06:34.090
You’re always gonna find street lights.

00:06:34.090 --> 00:06:38.190
So right here we have a nice street light
and there’s a few of them all along this

00:06:38.190 --> 00:06:39.190
road.

00:06:39.190 --> 00:06:40.190
There’s another one right here.

00:06:40.190 --> 00:06:44.200
So this street, is well lit at night.

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:46.390
You noticed I just called it a road.

00:06:46.390 --> 00:06:52.410
I think that’s because I live in the country
and it’s easier to refer to this that way.

00:06:52.410 --> 00:06:54.880
But this is a street, it’s definitely a
street.

00:06:54.880 --> 00:06:57.460
It is a city street.

00:06:57.460 --> 00:06:58.680
Sidewalk.

00:06:58.680 --> 00:07:00.250
Bike lane.

00:07:00.250 --> 00:07:02.150
Street lights.

00:07:02.150 --> 00:07:06.400
So behind me you can see the highway.

00:07:06.400 --> 00:07:08.990
This is a six lane highway.

00:07:08.990 --> 00:07:11.170
It has three lanes going in either direction.

00:07:11.170 --> 00:07:18.139
If you look over here it’s a little hard
to see but you can see the off ramp.

00:07:18.139 --> 00:07:24.170
The off ramp is what allows traffic to get
off the highway, and if you look over here

00:07:24.170 --> 00:07:27.910
you can just sort of see the on ramp.

00:07:27.910 --> 00:07:33.750
The on ramp is where you can speed up to get
on the highway.

00:07:33.750 --> 00:07:36.930
I’m standing on what we would call an overpass.

00:07:36.930 --> 00:07:43.340
